        },
        "3": {
          "id": "EC13",
          "title": "3",
          "desc":
            "The defense of UBI offered here is not, however, primarily about social justice as such. It is about creating the conditions under which a stable move toward more equal power within class relations can be achieved.",
          "infograph": [
            {
              "imgsrc": "blah",
