          "links": ["link", "link", "link"]
        },
        "2": {
          "id": "EC22",
          "title": "2",
          "desc":
            "Government borrowing costs are lower, so the government could lend money to the private sector and take a margin on the difference in interest rates.",
          "infograph": [
