          "links": ["link", "link", "link"]
        },
        "3": {
          "id": "EC23",
          "title": "3",
          "desc":
            "The state could also manage projects itself to save money on future subsidies to the private sector. If the projects are profit-making, the government could keep the profit and use it to lower taxes, pay off the national debt or finance a better country.",
          "infograph": [
            {
              "imgsrc": "blah",
