          ],
          "links": ["link", "link", "link"]
        },
        "4": {
          "id": "EC34",
          "title": "4",
          "desc":
            "Funding a proper bus service, area by area, would fuel a cultural shift towards relying on public transport instead of cars, reducing traffic and making buses more reliable and cheaper. Funding a fast broadband rollout and good public transport would reduce the pressure to live in the towns with good broadband and train connections.",
          "infograph": [
